//                       ready/scripts/verify_and_tune.py + bench.py --verify)
//   --verify --help     show verify usage
//   --verify <report>   validate a JSON verification report against SSOT thresholds
//                       exit 0 = PASS 7/7, exit 1 = FAIL
//
// Test categories (203 files):
//   consciousness: test_consciousness_*.py (anesthesia, hub, laws, meter, transplant, ...)
//   engine:        test_anima_alive.py, test_anima_unified.py, test_closed_loop.py
